OL,7,FA roofer from Wantage in Oxfordshire
OL,8,Fsays he's been left thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds out of pocket after thieves
OL,10,Fbroke into his work van in Eynsham on
OL,11,FTuesday night to steal all his tools.
OL,13,FHis van is one of a number of vehicles
OL,14,Fbroken into in the area that night.
OL,16,FIt comes just two months after a
OL,17,Fsimilar spate of thefts in nearby
OL,18,FCarterton.
